comment_data.body:
@csells @InMatrix for input on verbiage

@DanTup sent an example over to me that looked like this:
![Screen Shot 2021-01-25 at 2 14 15 PM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/43759233/105772884-ba55be00-5f17-11eb-8e17-2a51a2919d5d.png)

I think we should try to use consistent wording between the two IDEs, and I actually like how in this screenshot it just grabs the error message directly from the error, so it's consistent with console output as well.

For the button text, I like "Inspect widget"

